data.name: FrmFilterNormalMode_lblTitle
data.value:
After collecting according to the cycle conditions, the available option is Hunan Filter. Also, enter the cycle validity period.
Cycle Trigger condition: Prerequisite for detecting Cycle start Case 1. In the case of'Check for each cycle': Always check whether the set condition is satisfied before starting the cycle Case 2. In case of'Check only the latest cycle': When the first collection starts and the conditions are satisfied, the trigger is no longer checked.
Cycle start condition: The condition that the cycle starts Case 1. When the cycle start condition is set: When the trigger setting condition and the cycle start condition are satisfied, it is judged as the cycle start. Case 2. When the cycle start condition is not set: It is judged that the cycle starts when the time passes by the trigger setting condition and the cycle time setting value.
Cycle end condition: The condition that the cycle ends or restarts Case 1. When the cycle start condition is set. After the cycle start, if the trigger setting condition and the cycle start condition are satisfied again, restart the cycle. Case 2. When the cycle start condition is not set: After the cycle starts, if the trigger setting condition is satisfied and the cycle time setting value has elapsed, the cycle restart trigger setting condition is not satisfied, and if the time elapses, the cycle ends
